| GIA 1ct D-VS2 at $2,423 | $2,423 | Platinum V-tip $1,100 | $3,523 | $1,477 for band |
| Lab 2ct D-VVS1 ~$1,500 | ~$1,500 | Platinum V-tip $1,100 | ~$2,600 | $2,400 for band |

The [GIA 1ct G-VS1](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29379023?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) in platinum is the strongest natural option: $3,636 total for a GIA-certified 1ct platinum princess ring — $1,364 under the $5K budget, which covers a diamond wedding band or eternity ring.

